{"type": "article", "id": 16293, "title": "NikeLab Payaa", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-20T06:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 113, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135111AfXyZQ7cz1WxHs38.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNikeLab 发布了秋季新品 Payaa，灵感源于阿拉斯加原住民的 Payaaqek 靴。大面积采用透气的网眼布料，坡形的橡胶底和抽绳鞋带让鞋子舒适透气，在橡胶底的侧面用浮雕做标志，很帅气。有黑、白、桃红和蓝色四种，售价 80 美元，<a href=\"http://store.nike.com/us/en_us/pd/nikelab-payaa-unisex-shoe/pid-10327657/pgid-11100533\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143638l91JFDPo8ISBTKhM.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143638QCVIbdYi5AFKlPwr.jpg\" width=\"848\" height=\"1024\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.20754717\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143639Ys0A8yQ5CEWgtFqr.jpg\" width=\"660\" height=\"440\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143640urjcZmA178q2UTkR.jpg\" width=\"593\" height=\"360\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60708263\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143640FSezd10Awig2Ks9h.jpg\" width=\"589\" height=\"330\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56027165\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}